To deploy dev django project the first time:
 - git clone
 - [create virtual env and activate it] or [use --user]
Then:
 - python setup.py sdist
 - pip install dist/meteography-0.1.tar.gz
Or:
 - pip install -e .
Note about requirements: system distrib may be easier
Then:
 - cd website/
 - mkdir data cams
 - create DB: 'python manage.py migrate'
 - create super user: 'python manage.py createsuperuser'

Use:
 - run server: from website run 'python manage.py runserver'
 - Go to admin section: http://<your domaine or IP>/admin
 - log in with superuser
 - add a webcam
 - add a prediction params
 - send snapshots to the REST API

Production:
 - To be documented. Contact me if in doubt.